## 🚀 Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (v14 or higher)
- npm or yarn

### Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/ginesys-sales-manager.git
cd ginesys-sales-manager

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the development server
npm start
```

The app will open at `http://localhost:3000`

